subject: Tennis
Australian Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Fernando Verdasco advanced to the quarterfinals of the Australian Open Monday, as did Rafael Nadal, the world’s No. 1 men’s player, and Jo-Wilfried Tsonga, last year’s runner-up.
